casebody.head_matter:
IN RE Kirk Wayne MCBRIDE, Sr., Petitioner
No. 18-9452
Supreme Court of the United States.
October 7, 2019
Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pauperis denied, and the petition for a writ of mandamus dismissed. See Rule 39.8.
